                            { icon: Users, label: "Relationships", desc: "Build deep connections and a powerful network that supports your vision and personal growth." },
                            { icon: Briefcase, label: "Work", desc: "Refine your professional output and systems to achieve more in less time with higher impact." },
                            { icon: Sun, label: "Life", desc: "Design a lifestyle of balance, purpose, and fulfillment that aligns with your core values." },
                        ].map((item, i) => (
                            <div key={i} className="bg-[#efefec] p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-[#2b2b2b]/5 text-left flex flex-col hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                                <div className="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style={{ backgroundColor: 'rgba(123, 3, 35, 0.1)' }}>
                                    <item.icon className="w-5 h-5" style={{ color: '#7b0323' }} />
                                </div>
                                <h3 className="text-lg font-bold mb-2">{item.label}</h3>
                                <p className="opacity-60 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
                            </div>
                        ))}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </Section>

            {/* Brand Banner */}
            <div className="w-full py-16 px-6" style={{ backgroundColor: '#7b0323' }}>
                <div className="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
                    <p className="mb-10 text-white/90 text-xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        By integrating these pillars into your daily routine, you create a flywheel effect where each area of your life strengthens the others. This isn't just about professional success; it's about building a holistic life that you are proud to lead.
                    </p>
                    <WhiteButton onClick={handleApplyClick}>Apply Now</WhiteButton>
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* Secondary Hero Section */}
            <Section className="py-12">
                <div className="bg-[#f7f5f2] p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-[#2b2b2b]/5 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div className="space-y-6 md:col-span-2 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
                        <p className="text-lg opacity-80 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
                            We understand that the journey to peak performance is unique for everyone. This specialized approach ensures that you're not just following a template, but creating a system that works specifically for your life and work demands.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div className="md:col-span-1 w-full h-full flex items-center">
                        <ImageFrame
                            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
                            alt="Team Meeting"
                            className="h-64 md:h-full min-h-[250px] w-full"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </Section>

            {/* Mastery Section */}
            <Section className="text-center">
                <div className="inline-block px-8 py-2 border border-[#2b2b2b]/20 rounded-full mb-10">
                    <h2 className="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold">This is how your life will level up</h2>
                </div>
                <div className="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    {[
                        { n: 1, img: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506126613408-eca07ce68773?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80', title: 'Phase 1 Mastery' },
