                                    </div>
                                    <div className="text-center md:text-left">
                                        <h3 className="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#2b2b2b] tracking-tight mb-1">{selectedTestimonial.name}</h3>
                                        <div className="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start space-x-2">
                                            <span className="h-px w-3 bg-[#7b0323]/30 hidden md:block"></span>
                                            <p className="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold text-[#7b0323] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">{selectedTestimonial.role}</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div className="hidden lg:block opacity-[0.03] transform">
                                    <Quote className="w-24 h-24" />
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div className="flex-grow overflow-y-auto px-6 md:px-16 pb-12 pt-4 testimonial-scroll">
                            <div className="relative">
                                <div className="absolute -top-10 -left-6 text-[10rem] text-[#7b0323]/5 font-serif select-none pointer-events-none leading-none">“</div>
                                <div className="space-y-6 text-[#2b2b2b]/80 italic leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg whitespace-pre-wrap relative z-10 font-medium">
                                    {selectedTestimonial.text}
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div className="h-8 w-full"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            )}

            {/* Who is this for? */}
            <Section className="text-center bg-[#f7f5f2] rounded-3xl mx-6 md:mx-auto mb-16 shadow-inner py-16">
                <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b2b2b] mb-12">Who is this for?</h2>
                <div className="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10 text-left">
                    {[
                        { t: "The Action Taker", d: "You are ready to put in the work and stop making excuses." },
                        { t: "The Visionary", d: "You have a big goal but need the structural roadmap to get there." },
                        { t: "The Scaler", d: "You already have momentum but want to 10x your current results." }
                    ].map((item, i) => (
                        <div key={i} className="bg-[#efefec] p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-[#2b2b2b]/5 hover:border-[#7b0323]/30 transition-colors group">
                            <h3 className="font-bold text-lg mb-2 group-hover:text-[#7b0323] transition-colors">{item.t}</h3>
                            <p className="opacity-60 text-sm">{item.d}</p>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
                <Button onClick={handleApplyClick}>Apply Now</Button>
            </Section>

            {/* Unified About Section */}
            <Section>
                <div className="bg-[#f7f5f2] rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-[#2b2b2b]/5 overflow-hidden">
                    <div className="p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
                        <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold" style={{ color: '#7b0323' }}>The Person Behind The Plan</h2>
                        <p className="opacity-50 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold mt-2">Your Mentor & Guide</p>
                    </div>

                    <div className="grid md:grid-cols-3 items-stretch">
                        <div className="md:col-span-2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <h3 className="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">My Journey to Mastery</h3>
                            <div className="space-y-4 opacity-80 leading-relaxed">
                                <p>Hi, I'm the creator of this methodology. I spent years figuring out the exact steps required to achieve sustainable success. What started as a personal quest for efficiency turned into a repeatable system for high-level performance.</p>
                                <p>I believe that true growth happens when you align your professional ambitions with your personal values. I've coached hundreds of leaders to reclaim their time and double their impact without sacrificing their well-being.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div className="md:col-span-1 p-8">
                            <ImageFrame
                                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
                                alt="Mentor Profile"
                                className="w-full h-full min-h-[250px]"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div className="grid md:grid-cols-3 items-stretch pb-8">
                        <div className="md:col-span-1 p-8 order-2 md:order-1">
                            <ImageFrame
                                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80"
                                alt="Mentoring in Action"
                                className="w-full h-full min-h-[250px]"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div className="md:col-span-2 p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center order-1 md:order-2">
                            <div className="space-y-4 opacity-80 leading-relaxed">
                                <p>Now, my mission is to help dedicated individuals shortcut their path and achieve in months what took me years. We focus on the high-leverage activities that move the needle while removing the friction that holds you back.</p>
                                <p className="font-semibold text-[#2b2b2b]">Let's build something amazing together. Your transformation starts with a single, decisive step today.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </Section>

            {/* FAQ Section */}
            <Section className="py-24">
                <div className="bg-[#f7f5f2] rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-[#2b2b2b]/5 shadow-sm">
                    <div className="text-center mb-10">
                        <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b2b2b] tracking-tight mb-2">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div className="space-y-2">
                        {faqs.map((faq, index) => {
                            const isOpen = openFaq === index;
                            return (
                                <div
                                    key={index}
                                    className={`faq-item border-b border-[#2b2b2b]/5 last:border-none transition-all duration-300 ${isOpen
                                        ? 'bg-white shadow-sm rounded-2xl px-6 mb-3'
                                        : 'px-4 hover:bg-[#7b0323]/5 hover:rounded-xl'
                                        }`}
                                >
                                    <button onClick={() => toggleFaq(index)} className="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center group">
                                        <span className={`text-base font-semibold transition-all ${isOpen ? 'text-[#7b0323]' : 'text-[#2b2b2b] group-hover:text-[#7b0323]'}`}>
                                            {faq.q}
                                        </span>
                                        <ChevronDown className={`w-4 h-4 transition-transform ${isOpen ? 'rotate-180 text-[#7b0323]' : 'text-[#2b2b2b]/30 group-hover:text-[#7b0323]'}`} />
                                    </button>
                                    <div className={`faq-content ${isOpen ? 'open' : ''}`}>
                                        <div className="text-[14px] opacity-70 leading-relaxed pb-4">{faq.a}</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            );
                        })}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </Section>

            {/* Final CTA */}
            <Section className="py-24 text-center">
                <div className="bg-[#f7f5f2] p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-[#2b2b2b]/5 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-center text-left mb-16">
                    <div className="space-y-6 md:col-span-2 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
                        <h2 className="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#2b2b2b]">Eliminate Stress & Perform At Your Peak</h2>
                    </div>
                    <ImageFrame src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493612276216-ee3925520721?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Ultimate Focus" className="h-64 md:h-full min-h-[250px] w-full" />
                </div>
                <div className="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                    <Button onClick={handleApplyClick}>Apply Now</Button>
                    <p className="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold text-[#2b2b2b]/40">
                        * Limited slots available
                    </p>
                </div>
            </Section>

            {/* Footer */}
            <footer className="py-12 px-6" style={{ backgroundColor: '#7b0323' }}>
                <div className="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div className="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 mb-8">
                        <div className="group flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:scale-110 cursor-pointer shadow-lg active:scale-95">
                            <Mail className="w-5 h-5 text-white/80 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[#7b0323]" />
                        </div>
                        <div className="group flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:scale-110 cursor-pointer shadow-lg active:scale-95">
                            <InstagramIcon className="w-5 h-5 text-white/80 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[#7b0323]" />
                        </div>
                        <div className="group flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:scale-110 cursor-pointer shadow-lg active:scale-95">
                            <YoutubeIcon className="w-5 h-5 text-white/80 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[#7b0323]" />
                        </div>
                        <div className="group flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:scale-110 cursor-pointer shadow-lg active:scale-95">
                            <LinkedinIcon className="w-5 h-5 text-white/80 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-[#7b0323]" />
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div className="flex items-center space-x-1 text-[#efefec]/60 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
                        <span>Made with</span> <Heart className="w-3 h-3 text-red-500 fill-red-500" /> <span>in India</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </footer>
        </div>
    );
}